message.body: Did you find a picture you liked of yourself for the profile you were setting up?
Hm, we'll have to start taking more pictures! What profile is it for?
Cool! I forgot to mention on the phone that Mom wanted to get together soon, we were thinking maybe to meet in Baltimore Saturday. You free to join?
I don't think I can make it this weekend. What's the plan for Sat?
Mom heard of some festival ... Not sure, but may drive there for the day
